            <h3><b>Builds Conceptual Understanding</b></h3>
                    <p style = "font-size: 14pt";>Helps students grasp key ideas like decomposition, abstraction, pattern recognition, and algorithms before applying them in code.

</p>
           </div>
    </div>

   
<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;">
        <img src="https://images.code.org/4fb6f376cc7f6dc32cb3dfe1833fb302-image-1741020271499.png" alt="gear with check mark" style="width: 20%; max-width: 120px; height: auto;">
        <div style="flex: 1; background: #f7f8fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); ">
            <h3> <b>Reduces Cognitive Load</b></h3>
           <p style = "font-size: 14pt";>Allows students to focus on problem-solving without worrying about programming syntax.
</p>
           </div>
    </div>

<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;">
