        <div style="flex: 1; background: #f7f8fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
            <h3><b>Encourages Collaboration</b></h3>
            <p style = "font-size: 14pt";>Many unplugged activities involve teamwork, fostering communication and critical thinking skills.
</p>
        </div>
    </div>

   
<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;">
